snippet.title: Space for Sale - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
The moment is finally here, Space for Sale is taking off!
Come along for the ride, by yourself or with a friend, and experience wild and goofy space realty adventures! 

Get the Game on Steam now! · https://store.steampowered.com/app/1624060/Space_for_Sale/
